{
  "stem": "25809.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Meanwhile, my sister got sick and tired of the whole thing, and she moved out of the house, which pleased my father to no end because he was very unhappy, and it was one mouth less to feed.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He started his business.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "His business started to-- to work all right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Every day I had to go from school, which finished at 4 o'clock, and go to the store, and I had to make whatever deliveries there were.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I had to make deliveries.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I got a bike.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My father got me a bike, and I would make deliveries on a bicycle all over Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There was just no stopping.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Wherever there was a delivery to made-- to be made, I made the delivery on my bicycle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we had chinaware and crystal and leather goods and all that stuff, more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And people needed presents to be delivered.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I was the token delivery boy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It seems strange.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's like you started life all over again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody recognized me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody said, hey, I remember you, or what happened to you?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's-- it was-- here were four years or five years out of my life that were literally taken away that didn't seem to exist for a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I existed, but I did not exist for others.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was no way of recapturing that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My-- I had no youth to speak of.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All I did was just be in a little room most of the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my best time was when I was in Achttienhoven when I could leave and walk into the-- into the meadows, which I would do over and over and over again, except when it got cold.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And unfortunately, I didn't have-- hardly had any shoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
